<item>
            <title>[LU-14834] List the UUIDs of stale clients during a recovery</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14834</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be interesting to have the list of clients yet to be reconnected during a recovery. It would allow the user to check which clients are involved by looking into the logs prior to the failure of the server.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A possible implementation would involve the creation of a new entry in /proc next to recovery_status which would display them during the recovery.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
